text: The Sea () is a 2002 Icelandic French Norwegian comedy drama movie directed by Baltasar Kormákur and starring Gunnar Eyjólfsson, Hilmir Snær Guðnason, Hélène de Fougerolles, Kristbjörg Kjeld. == Other websites == * * Category:2002 comedy-drama movies Category:Icelandic movies Category:French comedy movies Category:French drama movies Category:Norwegian comedy movies Category:Norwegian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Baltasar Kormákur
